data.description: Live the Good life! This customized, maintenance free, end unit townhome is nestled in the quaint community of Sylvan Crossing in Lutz FL, Steinbrenner school district. The largest floorplan available and tucked in the back of the community for a private, peaceful location.  Boasting 1872 sq ft 3 bedroom, 2 bath, and 1/2 bath with a 2 car garage. The kitchen features beautiful cabinetry, quartz counter tops, custom backsplash and hood vent, and stainless steel appliances. Also, the best of the best - a separate coffee or wine bar. It also offers an expansive island for seating and more food prep space, all overlooking the dining and family rooms. Off the living room is a private screened in lanai.  The oversized owner’s suite has so much space, an amazing closet, with private en-suite bathroom.  The 2 additional bedrooms, loft and laundry facility are all conveniently located on the second level as well.  Just a short stroll to enjoy the community pool and club house facilities. This like new community is tucked away for ultimate privacy, but with the most convenient location close to shopping, restaurants, schools, and Florida's spectacular beaches.  See this one today!
